eligible to seek parole in 10 months based on precedent 
indelicato would likely serve 12 to 18 months in prison gants said 
the sentence handed down by us district court judge douglas 
woodlock was half the fiveyear term gants recommended but the 
judge said it was more severe than most similar cases 
