<TEXT>
the nations june unemployment rate fell to 53 percent its 
best level in nearly 14 years as youths flooded the job market 
and found a wealth of opportunity the government reported today 
the 03percentagepoint improvement from the previous month 
marked the first time the rate has dipped so strongly since 1986 
and sent it to its lowest since joblessness stood at 51 percent in 
