parliament late thursday said traffic growth is likely to 
accelerate as the eec deregulates the commercial airline industry 
in the next several years 
the resolution said overcongested airspace and limited airport 
capacity had led to delays not only causing major inconvenience 
to passengers but also reducing safety 
