common stock for each common share they currently own 
usg has historically carried a modest level of debt and while 
that is our preference present circumstances require that we 
provide an immediate return to shareholders said day we 
intend to reduce our debt load as rapidly as possible and are in a 
strong position to do so 
virtually all of the 20minute comment period friday on motions 
affecting shareholders was devoted to the recapitalization 
many said theyd made a lot of money in the past and were 
happy with the way things were said thomas sleeter manager of 
investor relations they didnt wany anybody to tamper 
the companys stock price had doubled over the past five years 
and was trading above 50 per share before octobers market crash 
when desert partners launched its 42pershare offer in march usg 
was trading below 30 
in trading on the new york stock exchange usg was up 62 cents 
a share at 49 by late afternoon 
day and usgs current management won the bitter protracted 
takeover battle but he acknowledged in an interview thursday that 
the price was a recapitalization that will inhibit usgs growth and 
restrict its resources for several years 
there are no winners in this were going into very heavy 
leverage and that has its negatives day said thursday we 
dont feel we lost but the whole process isnt one that gives us a 
great deal of satisfaction either 
as a result of the restructuring an unspecified number of jobs 
will be lost already the work force has been cut 9 percent this 
year day said 
two companies will be sold reversing a trend that saw usg 
acquire five companies in 1987 
it will restrict our ability to pay dividends to commit 
capital to capital investments and reduce our research and 
development program and these latter two in particular are the 
things which provide growth for the future day said 
he said the recapitalization was the only why to satisfy usgs 
loyal longterm investors and the newcomers who moved in on the 
heels of desert partners 
but he admitted he regrets the restructuring was necessary 
im not bitter but i am sorry day said its been very 
costly disruptive and demoralizing so its pretty hard to find 
anything to feel good about 
