petersen publishing co said it has acquired 
sport magazine for an undisclosed price the companies announced 
friday 
sport magazine a 900000circulation monthly founded in 1946 
carries indepth stories on spectator sports it had been owned 
privately and is based in new york 
petersen already publishes a pro sport series of magazines 
including pro football pro baseball and pro basketball it said 
those magazines will continue to be published in conjunction with 
sport magazine 
petersen which is privately owned also publishes 11 specialty 
magazines with a combined circulation of 39 million they include 
teen hot rod 4wheel and off road guns and ammo hunting 
fishing and skin diver 
